high_descs: Turn right and take two steps then turn right and walk to the red garbage.
Pick up the wine bottle that's in the garbage.
Turn right and take a step then turn right and walk to the fridge.
Chill the wine bottle in the fridge then get it back out and close the door.
Move to your right and stop when you get to the middle of the white table then take a step backwards.
Put the wine bottle near the edge of the table to the left of the bread.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold wine bottle on the table.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the the trash can.
Pick up the wine bottle from the trash can.
Turn around and walk to the the fridge.
place the wine bottle in the fridge, wait, and then remove the bottle.
Approach the table to the right of the fridge.
Place the wine bottle on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooled wine bottle on the table to the right of the fridge.

high_descs: Turn right, then turn around and walk to the red trash can.
Pick up the wine bottle from the trashcan.
Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Cool the wine bottle on the top shelf of the fridge, then pull it out again.
Walk to the white table to the right of the fridge.
Place the wine bottle on the left of the table, close to the edge.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooled wine bottle on a table.
